<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.4.9">
<l>nantaṉ matalai nilamaṅkai naltuṇaivaṉ</l>
<l>anta mutalva ṉamararkaḷ tamperumāṉ</l>
<l>kantam kamaḻkāyā vaṇṇaṉ katirmuṭimēl</l>
<l>kontu naṟuntuḻāy koṇṭūtāy kōltumpī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Twiggy dragonfly, clasp and sip from the fragrant tulasī cluster</l>
<l>On the shining crown of Nanda’s child, the good companion of lady earth,</l>
<l>The one who is the end and the beginning, the celestials’ great lord,</l>
<l>The one the color of kāyā [flowers] where fragrance wafts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
